%%{init: {"theme":"base","themeVariables":{"fontFamily":"Microsoft YaHei, Noto Sans CJK SC, sans-serif","background":"#F8FAFC","primaryTextColor":"#243447","actorBkg":"#EEF5FB","actorBorder":"#7198BF","signalColor":"#64748B"}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor OP as 操作员
    participant KWS as 本地 KWS / VoiceSession
    participant ASR as DashScope ASR
    participant AG as Inspection Agent
    participant LLM as LLM Planner
    participant SP as Schema / Policy
    participant TP as ToolPack
    participant SUP as Supervisor
    participant PN as Patrol Executor / Nav2
    participant HW as Robot Hardware
    participant OUT as UI / TTS

    Note over KWS,OUT: 语音节点、Planner 与 TTS 均可选启用；Agent 只暴露任务级工具，不开放 /cmd_vel 或原始 Nav2 goal
    OP->>KWS: 说出唤醒词“小零小零”
    KWS->>KWS: sherpa-onnx 本地 KWS + VAD
    KWS-->>OUT: /inspection_ai/voice_session_status
    OP->>KWS: 说出巡逻/状态/运动指令
    KWS->>ASR: HTTPS 上传临时 WAV，qwen3-asr-flash
    alt ASR 成功
        ASR-->>KWS: 识别文本
        KWS->>AG: /inspection_ai/agent_request
        AG->>LLM: OpenAI-compatible /chat/completions + AgentSpec
        LLM-->>AG: tool_call + arguments + speak
        AG->>SP: Agent chat schema 校验
        SP-->>AG: 结构合法 / 拒绝
        AG->>SP: Capability schema + Policy 前置条件校验
        SP-->>AG: allowed / precondition_failed / policy_rejected
        alt 校验通过
            AG->>TP: 执行受控工具
            Note over TP,HW: LLM 不直接发布 /cmd_vel；运动只能经 base_motion_skill 或 Supervisor→Patrol Executor→Nav2
            TP->>SUP: /inspection_ai/system_command（巡逻/急停/组件）
            opt 巡逻或检查点任务
                SUP->>PN: 准备 bringup、AMCL、TF、Nav2 后发布 /patrol/command
                PN->>HW: NavigateToPose → Nav2 /cmd_vel → 底盘 CANopen
            end
            TP-->>AG: sent + operation_id
            AG-->>OUT: agent_status = waiting_feedback
            loop operation_poll_sec 轮询真实反馈
                HW-->>PN: /odom、/scan、底盘状态
                PN-->>SUP: /patrol/status、/patrol/event
                SUP-->>AG: /inspection_ai/system_status 或 base_skill_status
            end
            alt 成功
                AG->>AG: OperationManager → succeeded
                AG-->>OUT: agent_event / agent_chat + 成功答复
            else 失败
                AG->>AG: OperationManager → failed / rejected
                AG-->>OUT: 错误码、原因与安全提示
            else 用户取消
                OP->>KWS: “取消巡逻/停止”
                KWS->>AG: 新的取消请求
                AG->>SUP: cancel_patrol / stop_motion
                SUP->>PN: 取消当前 goal，发布零速度
                PN-->>AG: canceled
                AG-->>OUT: 已取消
            else 超时
                AG->>AG: OperationManager → timeout
                AG->>SUP: timeout guard：cancel_patrol / stop_motion
                SUP->>PN: 取消导航并置零
                AG-->>OUT: 超时与已执行的安全收尾
            end
        else Schema 或 Policy 拒绝
            AG-->>OUT: agent_event = rejected + 原因
        end
    else ASR 空结果、失败或超时
        ASR-->>KWS: 空文本 / 错误 / timeout
        KWS-->>OUT: 重试提示；连续失败进入待唤醒
    end

    par 最终可视输出
        AG-->>OUT: /inspection_ai/agent_chat、agent_status、agent_event
    and 最终语音输出（可选）
        AG-->>OUT: /inspection_ai/say_text → DashScope TTS → ALSA
    end

    rect rgb(255, 241, 242)
        Note over OP,HW: 急停本地快速通道：无需等待 Planner 的后续步骤
        OP->>OUT: 点击本体 UI 软件急停
        OUT->>SUP: /inspection_ai/system_command = emergency_stop
        SUP->>HW: 连续发布 5 次零 Twist，并将 system_mode 置 fault
        SUP-->>OUT: system_status / system_mode
    end

